<troubleshooting id="troubleshooting-599" xml:lang="en-us" class="- topic/topic troubleshooting/troubleshooting "><title class="- topic/title ">This account has been blocked</title><troublebody class="- topic/body troubleshooting/troublebody "><troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution "><cause class="- topic/section troubleshooting/cause "><p class="- topic/p ">This error message indicates that your Katalon account has been registered but not yet verified.</p><p class="- topic/p ">Follow these steps to unblock your Katalon account:</p></cause><remedy class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy "><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Go to <xref href="https://katalon.com/" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">katalon.com</xref>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-step-1.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The Katalon website homepage.</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Access your account by clicking the log in link at the upper right corner. </cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-step-2.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The log-in button on the Katalon website. </alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the sign-in screen, enter your registered e-mail and password. </cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-step-3.png" width="850" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The sign-in screen for the Katalon Platform.</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-platform" class="- topic/ph "/> homepage, click on the profile button in the upper right corner. </cmd><substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps "><substep class="- topic/li task/substep "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click on the View Profile link.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-ste-4a_copy.jpg" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The user profile menu in the Katalon Platform.</alt></image></info></substep></substeps></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the new window displaying your profile details, click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Verify Email</uicontrol> button. </cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-step-5.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The verify email button in a user's profile.</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">A verification link is sent to your e-mail account. Follow the instructions in the e-mail. </cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image href="image/troubleshooting-599-step-6.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">The Katalon Platform sends a verification link out. </alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Once your account is verified, open <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> and it will reactivate.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><note class="- topic/note ">If activation still fails, wait for 5 minutes and try again.</note></info></step></steps></remedy></troubleSolution></troublebody></troubleshooting>